---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="EV Şarj & Danışmanlık | Solut Enerji"
  description="GES Danışmanlık Hizmetleri ve Elektrikli Araç Şarj altyapısı. Teknik mükemmellik ile sürdürülebilir inovasyonu birleştiriyoruz."
>
<main class="pt-20">
<!-- Hero Section: Kinetic Monolith -->
<section class="relative min-h-[819px] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-primary text-white">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-40">
<img alt="Electric vehicle charging station infrastructure" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Modern electric vehicle charging station architecture at dusk" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBve9dEsKBaDSOiRfLCO_8sP-lkl0hKAWzFznrzJL02iaVjSPq9NDVeoiYxi_iRMlVf3TroD6DPpMEd3-XnhPQZ2kaoUOUHaTsbY1PYNxBpb1joDC6M9BjPxCbaikRGrh61o3JUx3mEDqr2HJ3CduQ51XRQLpfYCeN10CgarR9Y3DK0_zGPdThPL6_QletTmid4mtWAhc48hVLGomKo2wMVbZdI04HSJEgsx8MZy6vuPvY05y5VmwwKo1Fp_kWecXW2-XzC9Hbz46o"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-primary/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
<div class="md:col-span-8">
<span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 rounded">
                        Next-Gen Energy Systems
                    </span>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
                        Engineering the <br/><span class="text-secondary-fixed-dim">Future of Power.</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-primary-fixed max-w-2xl mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
                        Solut Enerji provides end-to-end GES Danışmanlık Hizmetleri and Elektrikli Araç Şarj infrastructure, combining technical precision with sustainable innovation.
                    </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<button class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-sm transition-all hover:bg-secondary-fixed-dim active:scale-95">
                            Our Solutions
                        </button>
<button class="border border-outline-variant/30 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-sm glass-effect hover:bg-white/10 active:scale-95">
                            Expert Consultation
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- GES Danışmanlık: The Technical Authority -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface">
<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
<div class="md:col-span-5 sticky top-28">
<h2 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-secondary uppercase mb-4">Expertise</h2>
<h3 class="text-4xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary mb-6 leading-tight">
                            GES Danışmanlık Hizmetleri
                        </h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Navigating the complexities of solar energy requires more than just hardware. We provide the strategic engineering backbone for high-yield solar investments.
                        </p>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl">analytics</span>
<span class="font-semibold text-primary">Technical Due Diligence</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl">account_tree</span>
<span class="font-semibold text-primary">Grid Connection Management</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-7 grid gap-8">
<!-- Bento Grid for Consulting Features -->
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">query_stats</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-3">Energy Analysis</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Advanced yield forecasting and consumption modeling using high-precision meteorological data.</p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">assignment</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-3">Permitting &amp; Compliance</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">End-to-end legal and regulatory management, ensuring all projects meet international safety standards.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 p-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-xl flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
<div class="flex-1">
<h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold mb-3">Strategic Project Management</h4>
<p class="text-primary-fixed text-sm">From initial feasibility studies to final commissioning, our engineers ensure every kilowatt is optimized for ROI.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-4xl font-headline font-black text-secondary-fixed-dim">
                                    99.8% <span class="block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed text-right">Precision</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- EV Charging: The Kinetic Flow -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low overflow-hidden">
<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6">
<div class="max-w-xl">
<h2 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-secondary uppercase mb-4">Infrastructure</h2>
<h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary leading-tight">
                            Elektrikli Araç Şarj Çözümleri
                        </h3>
</div>
<div class="text-right">
<span class="text-6xl font-headline font-black text-outline-variant/30 leading-none">MOBILITY</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- AC/DC Solution Cards -->
<div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden group">
<div class="h-64 relative overflow-hidden">
<img alt="AC Charging Station" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="Modern residential AC EV charging unit installed on wall" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAdV-rFM4Dn3n62hNz42kcu5IEdVQOEdbD1eIayUZ-84cM-cFmNhpBTIiKvV6KWKVQ9uTthiWtMUSuUNXtaaB0Ialy-ul94KaIT4EQFAThcEFI5_9EOLNoKO6ltAmzdAiG4Fl3WhUirhdaCQmg8RYN00eYIW74JzxGvxz2ODeC9NMeAzVLfoK5KK11T41pWgkwx5sB9pqSN-XMPxQiTLv_3NA4gKW2r3EH_IRF-i2E8nzeMKRMA6NxEFJ4FbAG9pwa0epcwnjBpr-A"/>
<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full">Residential</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<h4 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-4">AC Charging Infrastructure</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-6">Optimized for workplaces and residential complexes, offering balanced load management and seamless user integration.</p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-secondary font-bold text-sm hover:underline" href="#">View Specs <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden group">
<div class="h-64 relative overflow-hidden">
<img alt="DC Charging Station" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="High power DC fast charger for electric cars" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAaMn2NLoAaxXEAMzdXCS1uTAOxXMm4HxRRHSU7IY1bWorPijcxakQVOMTj3fOSTM6KjB8v9bgMMfqtXWB1yOGZZCwd47wenVOssfnsCd-390rkDndD6VFtToltLmq0LkzH27G7hm2OsXf_HMgoYzu2H_F9rDPXgqgYI1v4ghHTUj6wFeNTdALrJG6wkRnpIofSJXuGqJEDxzJ_4021C5_sYGISyiYD1ZA1ELpBXAs5FNSHOaBwMnHacgODN9IXwquLmkTZHKPPdvQ"/>
<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-primary text-white px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full">Ultra-Fast</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<h4 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-4">DC Fast-Charging Hubs</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-6">Engineered for highways and commercial fleets, our DC solutions minimize downtime with up to 350kW charging capacity.</p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-secondary font-bold text-sm hover:underline" href="#">View Specs <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col bg-primary text-white rounded-xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 opacity-10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[12rem]">bolt</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold mb-6">Charge Management System (CMS)</h4>
<p class="text-primary-fixed text-sm mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                            A centralized dashboard for monitoring energy consumption, billing, and system health in real-time. Full OCPI &amp; OCPP compliance for universal roaming.
                        </p>
<div class="mt-auto space-y-3">
<div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-primary-container rounded-full overflow-hidden">
<div class="h-full bg-secondary-container w-3/4"></div>
</div>
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-primary-fixed">Real-time Load Balancing</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Asymmetric Data Visualization -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
<div class="md:col-span-7">
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute -left-12 -top-12 w-64 h-64 bg-secondary-container/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative bg-surface-container rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-8">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
<h5 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary">Regional Grid Impact</h5>
<span class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase">2024 Analysis</span>
</div>
<!-- Pseudo-Chart: The Data Monolith -->
<div class="flex items-end gap-2 md:gap-4 h-64">
<div class="flex-1 bg-primary/20 rounded-t-lg h-1/2"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-primary/40 rounded-t-lg h-3/4"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-secondary-container rounded-t-lg h-full"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-primary/60 rounded-t-lg h-2/3"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-primary/80 rounded-t-lg h-[85%]"></div>
</div>
<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-8">
<div>
<span class="block text-3xl font-headline font-black text-primary">500+</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider">Stations Deployed</span>
</div>
<div>
<span class="block text-3xl font-headline font-black text-primary">15MW+</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider">Managed Load</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-5">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary mb-6">Unrivaled Network <br/>Intelligence</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8">Our software-led approach to infrastructure means your energy assets aren't just connected; they're smart. We use AI to predict peak loads and adjust charging speeds across your entire portfolio.</p>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">check_circle</span>
<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">Dynamic Load Management (DLM)</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">check_circle</span>
<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">Vehicle-to-Grid (V2G) Integration</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">check_circle</span>
<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">Carbon Offset Reporting</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-20 px-6">
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-primary rounded-3xl p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/20 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-extrabold text-white mb-6">Ready to Power Your Assets?</h3>
<p class="text-primary-fixed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">Connect with our engineering team today for a comprehensive energy assessment and custom infrastructure design.</p>
<a href="/iletisim/" class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-10 py-5 rounded-md font-bold text-base transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-lg">Teknik Danışmanlık Al</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
